============================================================

Written to `tools/title-loop/docs/29-e7e3098/improvement-plan.md`.

**Summary of the plan — 6 changes targeting 8 of 9 failures:**

| Change | What | Fixes |
|--------|------|-------|
| **A** | Complete mixed-case OCR repair (`0→o`, `4→a`, `5→s`) | Patterns 1, 4, 7 |
| **B** | Garbled token detection in multi-word candidates | Pattern 3 |
| **C** | Expand Polish cooking verb filter (`ugotuj`, `podawać`, etc.) | Patterns 2, 4 |
| **D** | OCR normalization before instruction check (`Podaw4ć` → `Podawać`) | Pattern 2 |
| **E** | Strengthen positional bonus for post-metadata candidates | Pattern 5 |
| **F** | Strip trailing `(N)` page/step references | Pattern 4 (supporting) |

Pattern 6 (Mushroom Risotto — title absent from document) is acknowledged as unfixable without page-level context.

The changes are all O(1) per candidate — no new embedding calls or pipeline restructuring needed. The existing architecture (MiniLM embeddings + heuristic scoring) is working well; these are targeted fixes for specific gaps in the OCR repair and hard filter layers.
