{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01TerEcWSzeBxQwKhPzUwc6n","type":"tool_result","content":"ARAYES SHRAK | ARAYES SHRAK - yes\nBaked Eggs with Feta, Harissa Tomato Sauce & Coriander | Baked Eggs with Feta, Harissa Tomato Sauce & Coriander - yes\nCHLEBEK Z WARZYWAMI I BOCZKIEM | CHLEBEK Z WARZYWAMI I BOCZKIEM - yes\nFINNISH MILK FLATBREADS + FINNISH POTATO FLATBREADS | FINNISH MILK FLATBREADS + FINNISH POTATO FLATBREADS - yes\nFaszerowana papryka | Faszerowana papryka PAPRIKA GYERAN-JJIM 파프리카 계란찜 - yes\nKREM SELEROWY Z GORGONZOLA | KREM SELEROWY Z GORGONZOLA - yes\nLABANEH BALLS WITH NIGELLA SEEDS | LABANEH BALLS WITH NIGELLA SEEDS - yes\nMIXED SEED CRISPBREAD | MIXED SEED CRISPBREAD - yes\nOVERNIGHT STRAIGHT PIZZA DOUGH | OVERNIGHT STRAIGHT PIZZA DOUGH - yes\nSAFFRON WHEAT BUNS WITH QUARK : COTTAGE CHEESE (VARIATION D) | SAFFRON WHEAT BUNS WITH QUARK / COTTAGE CHEESE (VARIATION D) - yes\nSmażona zielona fasolka | Smażona zielona fasolka - yes","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01QxrA3xJSbnshGa1Pt2TJYu","session_id":"c37a3300-1904-44e6-bf34-65ba8b38fada","uuid":"ac4487a0-6eab-4caf-bb7f-c058305c3afa"}
